title: [Vtasia's Weaponry]
description: Beneath a vaulted ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the smooth granite walls.  Some wrought-iron hooks and a low wrought iron table sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an enameled hardwood floor.

Beneath a vaulted ceiling, a portrait of Darkstone Castle hangs on one of the smooth granite walls.  Some wrought-iron hooks and a low wrought iron table sit in opposite corners while a bronzed drake sculpture rests on an enameled hardwood floor.
